rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0001
rows.name:
So Acedia is gone, huh?
All the people who came from there are
all at a total loss...

rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0002
rows.name: It's not just that their home is gone...

rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0003
rows.name: They say having their faith betrayed is even harder.

rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0004
rows.name:
That's why I'm swimming with the kids who evacuated here,
to cheer them up!

rows.label: tlk41100121_05_msg0005
rows.name:
'Cause I learned that if we become friends and swim together,
we won't have to feel anxious anymore!
